data.description: Built less than one year ago!  This home is Conveniently located near historic Deland and close to I4 with quick access to Orlando going west and the World’s Most Famous Beach – Daytona Beach going east!  Welcome to this spacious one owner home with a great open floor plan and four bedrooms.  Kitchen features granite countertop with a large island and modern stainless steel appliances.  Master bedroom has vinyl flooring and an ensuite bath with raised double sink vanity and a walk in closet.  Inside laundry room with washer and dryer already in place.  Don’t wait, this one won’t last!  The AV disclosure attached, there are front and rear cameras that are motion activated.
